hints.description: This company is a leading owner and operator of single-family rental homes in the United States, primarily targeting the growing market of American renters. They manage a large portfolio of properties across various states, offering residents a homeownership alternative with amenities and services. CEO Jerry **** has overseen significant growth and expansion in the single-family rental sector.
hints.funFact1: The company was initially formed as a joint venture between Blackstone and Invitation Homes Trust in 2012, quickly becoming one of the largest players in the burgeoning single-family rental market following the 2008 financial crisis.
hints.funFact2: As of 2023, the company owns over ***** homes, representing a substantial portion of the institutional single-family rental market and demonstrating a significant shift in housing trends.
